{"tid":2318180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好鄰舍北區教會：本會帳目清晰 無懼對簿公堂","createTime":"2020-12-09T06:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T13:26:03.000Z","uid":12223,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c99e6081219c6117136779aeec4e922d38594cef","tid":2318180,"uid":12223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"本會帳目清晰<br />\n無懼對簿公堂<br />\n<br />\n警方所謂的「洗黑錢罪」只是障眼法，實質就是政權赤裸裸的打壓。政治清算從政治人物漫延至群眾﹕今天受逼迫的是教會及社福團體，明天遭欺壓的就是每個仍然堅守公義的群眾。<br />\n<br />\n本會前董事及職員仍在警方手上，對此全體同工及教友都深表擔憂及憤怒。作為教會及社福團體的其中一員，最令人痛心的是一直服侍的無家者和弱勢社群要因政治打壓而受苦。想到無家者失去「我們的家」，想到那即將失落的服務承諾&hellip;連累基層弱勢絕不是應得的結果。<br />\n<br />\n本會每年都會聘請專業會計師進行核數，以確保符合政府規定的慈善團體牌照的資格，所以警方空洞粗疏的指控絕不會成立。香港司法正步入黑暗深淵，然而我們堅信本會得清白之時，就是香港重光之日。<br />\n<br />\n「唯願公平如大水滾滾，使公義如江河滔滔。」阿摩司書 五章廿四節<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2456531847974509/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1561265357501167%2Fposts%2F2456531847974509%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=00d2947a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2456531847974509/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話董事咁後生，傳道人挾帶私逃，捐款落自己袋班人請問去曬邊？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地正氣到咁點私地你地班五毛見錢開眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6456d6d85d5446f3c5575afe7b261385807f8c","tid":2318180,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />G Chi"},{"pid":"cca74030acf05ef084f825dace957d1b4cd45144","tid":2318180,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"重對簿公堂？死得重快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27627be06e7c726c57d9b337c43d6b593fad301b","tid":2318180,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"港共狗：搬核數師出嚟吖嗱，等我連牌都釘撚咗佢等你份報告唔知邊撚個核，睇你到時仲嘈乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02176e7c2634b6295f63344bc441c6867af5c9e3","tid":2318180,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"true"}]}